}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "1242-01000340-50Z" is silkscreened on the board in the [https://fccid.io/document.php?id=1768751 FCC photos]. :Defualt settings are per the FCC manual and label.
{{see also|ASUS RT-N10#See also|Edimax}}
===Specifications=== *Product Segment: N150 (150Mbps) *Antenna: 1x fixed dipole antenna (5dBi) *Operating Frequency: 2.4 GHz *Ports: :LAN: 4x FE (RJ45) for 10/100 BaseT for LAN :WAN: 1x FE (RJ45) for 10/100 BaseT for WAN *Button: WPS Button, Reset Button, Power Button *Power Supply: :AC Input : 110~240V (50~60Hz) :DC Output : 12V with max. 0.5A current *Dimensions: 168 x 124 x 30 mm (WxDxH)
